statement:
Answer the following multiple choice question. Check your answer very
carefully. Your answer will be marked right or wrong (work will not be
considered for this problem).

The value of the integral

\[\int_0^{\infty} x^2 e^{-x} \,dx\] is

\begin{description}
\itemsep1pt\parskip0pt\parsep0pt
\item[]
A. $e-1$
\end{description}

\begin{description}
\itemsep1pt\parskip0pt\parsep0pt
\item[]
B. $2e-1$
\end{description}

\begin{description}
\itemsep1pt\parskip0pt\parsep0pt
\item[]
C. $0.5e$
\end{description}

\begin{description}
\itemsep1pt\parskip0pt\parsep0pt
\item[]
D. $1$
\end{description}

\begin{description}
\itemsep1pt\parskip0pt\parsep0pt
\item[]
E. $2$
\end{description}
